# redundant-arm-3d

Interactive 3D browser app where you drag a redundant robot arm's end effector through space and use a slider to explore null space reconfiguration — the arm reshapes while the gripper stays perfectly still.

---

## Tech Stack
- Vite (vanilla JS, no React, no TypeScript)
- Three.js (npm, ES module imports)
- No other dependencies

## Setup
```
npm create vite@latest . -- --template vanilla
npm install three
```

## File Structure
```
redundant-arm-3d/
